---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutMeImage from '../assets/aboutme/BrunoGambLogo.webp';
---

<section id="aboutme" class="aboutme-section">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i>Sobre mí</h2>

    <div class="aboutme-container">
        <div class="info-container">
            <p><span>Desarrollador web </span> especializado en crear interfaces rápidas y escalables con Astro. Cuento con experiencia real digitalizando negocios y optimizando flujos de trabajo. Enfocado en la performance, el código limpio y soluciones que impacten en el usuario final.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://github.com/Brunogamb" target="_blank" aria-label="GitHub"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> GitHub</a>
                <a href="mailto:brunogamberini24@gmail.com" target="_blank" aria-label="Email"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Email</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <Image src={aboutMeImage} alt="Foto de perfil de Bruno Gamb" />
    </div>
    
    <div class="technologies-section">
        <div class="technologies-grid">
            <div class="technology-card">
                <div class="technology-icon">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-html5"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="technology-content">
                    <div class="technology-name">HTML</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technology-card">
                <div class="technology-icon">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-css3-alt"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="technology-content">
                    <div class="technology-name">CSS</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technology-card">
                <div class="technology-icon">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-js-square"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="technology-content">
                    <div class="technology-name">JavaScript</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technology-card">
                <div class="technology-icon">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="technology-content">
                    <div class="technology-name">Astro</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technology-card">
                <div class="technology-icon">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="technology-content">
                    <div class="technology-name">Supabase</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<style>
.aboutme-section {
    min-height: 90vh; 
    height: auto;     
    padding: 60px 0;   
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.aboutme-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    align-items: center;
}

.aboutme-container img {  
    max-width: 260px;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-left: 40px;
    border: 3px solid var(--accent-cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.2);
}

.info-container span {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
}

.info-container p {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-wrap: balance;
}

.social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-top: 24px;
}

.social-links a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    transition: var(--transition);
}

h2 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 32px;
    gap: 12px;
    max-width: 900px;
    padding: 0 20px;
}

.technologies-section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 50px auto 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
}

.technologies-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
}

.technology-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: var(--transition);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

.technology-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent-cyan-alpha), transparent);
    transition: left 0.6s ease;
}

.technology-icon {
    width: 55px;
    height: 55px;
    background: var(--accent-cyan-alpha);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
    transition: var(--transition);
}

.technology-icon i {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.4));
}

.technology-name {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
}

@media (hover: hover) {
    .social-links a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
        border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
        background-color: var(--accent-cyan-alpha);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .technology-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
        background: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.05);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .technology-card:hover::before {
        left: 100%;
    }

    .technology-card:hover .technology-icon {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .aboutme-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 30px;
    }
    
    .aboutme-container img {
        margin-left: 0;
        order: -1;
        max-width: 200px;
    }

    .aboutme-section {
        padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .info-container p {
        font-size: 1rem; 
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 90%;
        margin: auto;
    }

    .social-links {
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column; 
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .social-links a {
        justify-content: center;
        width: 100%; 
    }

    .technologies-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); 
        gap: 15px;
    }

    .technology-card {
        padding: 20px 15px;
    }

    .technology-icon i {
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    .technology-name {
        font-size: 1.1rem; 
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 26px;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
}
</style>